Revert "Update aws_thing_loop.py"

Use standard ntptime library; speed up get_ntp loop; work around tim.init on soft reset.

return time_tuple to aws_thing_loop instead of timestamp to push more machine specific code to the thing.

missing key [state] in _reported_state_get
fix thing.reported_state getting called twice
